export const COLORS = {
    white: '#fff',
    black: '#000',
    primary: '#5DBB4A',
    transparentPrimary: 'rgba(#5DBB4A, 0.1)',
    secondary: '#F1F5F4',
    transparent: 'transparent',
    transparentBlack1: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)",
    transparentBlack2: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)",
    transparentBlack3: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)"
  }
